      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in exceptional condition. This vehicle features the S54B32 3.2L inline-six power plant, meticulously maintained with a proactive rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is structurally sound, featuring a documented rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension retains its factory-spec handling characteristics with crisp turn-in and zero bushing deflection. Every mechanical component, from the individual throttle bodies to the dual-VANOS timing, operates within original tolerances. This is a rare, mechanically flawless specimen for the discerning purist.",
